content: yungalgo: Focused on improving the user experience and content within the `elizaos/docs` repository, merging five pull requests. Their most impactful work included adding a new 'launch resources' page (#76) which involved a significant content refactor, renaming the API Reference section for clarity (#75), and fixing broken plugin links (#74). This work, along with several comments on issues, demonstrates a clear focus on documentation improvements and bug fixes.
